<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<span class="color_11 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">_Last Updated: 09/01/2024<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**1. Introduction**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Welcome to Exportunity.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- This Privacy Policy applies to all Exportunity apps, including our custom GPTs.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Our commitment to your privacy.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**2. Information We Collect**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Personal identification information (Name, email address, phone number, etc.).<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Usage data (app usage patterns, preferences, etc.).<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Data collected through GPT interactions.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- How data is collected (directly provided, through app usage, etc.).<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**3. Lawful Basis for Processing Personal Data**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Compliance with GDPR, CCPA, and other regulations.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Data processing for legitimate business purposes.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Consent-based processing.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**4. How We Use Your Data**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- To provide and maintain our services.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- For customer support and communication.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- To improve and personalize user experiences.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Legal obligations and data analysis.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**5. Data Sharing and Disclosure**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Situations where we might share data with third parties (service providers, legal requirements, etc.).<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Assurance of no selling of personal data.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**6. Data Security**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Measures taken to protect data (encryption, secure servers, etc.).<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Data breach response protocol.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**7. Data Retention**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- How long we keep data.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Data deletion procedures.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**8. International Data Transfers**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Information about cross-border data transfers.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Safeguards for international data protection.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**9. Your Data Protection Rights**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- GDPR rights: Access, correction, deletion, etc.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- CCPA rights: Access, opt-out of sale, etc.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- How to exercise these rights.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**10. Special Considerations for GPT Interactions**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Usage of AI and implications for data privacy.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Ensuring AI ethics and compliance in data handling.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**11. Children&rsquo;s Privacy**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Compliance with the Children&rsquo;s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA).<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Age limits and parental consent requirements.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**12. Changes to This Privacy Policy**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Rights to modify the policy.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- Notification process for changes.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
**13. Contact Us**<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
&nbsp; &nbsp;- How users can contact us for privacy-related inquiries.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
---<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
This outline serves as a framework. It&#39;s crucial to consult with a legal expert specializing in data protection and privacy laws to ensure full compliance and adequacy of the policy for Exportunity&#39;s specific operational scope and geographical reach.</span></span></h2></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></main><div id="soapAfterPagesContainer" class="page-without-sosp page-without-sosp"><div data-mesh-id="soapAfterPagesContainerinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="soapAfterPagesContainerinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><div id="CONTROLLER_COMP_CUSTOM_ID" style="display:none"></div></div></div></div><footer class="SITE_FOOTER_WRAPPER" tabindex="-1" id="SITE_FOOTER_WRAPPER"><div id="pinnedBottomRight" class="pinnedBottomRight"><div id="comp-km0rxgme-pinned-layer" class="comp-km0rxgme-pinned-layer big2ZD"><div id="comp-km0rxgme" class="OQ8Tzd comp-km0rxgme pvlz2w"><iframe class="nKphmK" title="Wix Chat" aria-label="Wix Chat" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="" allowtransparency="true" allowvr="true" frameBorder="0" allow="autoplay;camera;microphone;geolocation;vr"></iframe></div></div></div><div id="SITE_FOOTER" class="xU8fqS SITE_FOOTER wixui-footer" tabindex="-1"><div class="_C0cVf"><div class="_4XcTfy" data-testid="screenWidthContainerBg"></div></div><div class="U4Bvut"><div class="G5K6X8"><div class="gUbusX" data-testid="screenWidthContainerBgCenter"></div></div><div class="CJF7A2"><div data-mesh-id="SITE_FOOTERinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="SITE_FOOTERinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><div id="comp-km0rx7ev1" class="HcOXKn c9GqVL QxJLC3 comp-km0rx7ev1 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_10 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.79em;
